import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Devices from '../components/Devices/Devices'
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
import Singin from '../components/SignIn/Signin'
import MainLayout from '../container/MainLayout'
import AdDevices from '../components/Devices/AdDevices'
import UsDevices from '../components/Devices/UsDevices'
import MaDevices from '../components/Devices/MaDevices'
import Tracking from '../components/Devices/Tracking'
import MaUsers from '../components/User/MaUsers'
import DeviHistory from '../components/Devices/DeviHistory'
import { ProtectedRoute } from '../routes/ProtectedRoute'
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
export default function MainRouter() {
    return (
        <Router>
            <Switch>
                <Route exact path='/' component={Singin} />
                {/* <Route path='/db'> */}
                <MainLayout>
                    <Switch>
                        {/* --------------ADMIN ROUTER--------------------- */}
                        <Route path='/db/devices' component={Devices} />
                        <ProtectedRoute path='/db/manage-devices' component={MaDevices} />
                        <Route path='/db/manage-users' component={MaUsers} />
                        <Route path='/db/tracking' component={Tracking} />
                        <Route path='/db/u-devives' component={UsDevices} />
                        {/* ---------------USER ROUTER------------------------ */}
                        <Route path='/db/devives' component={AdDevices} />
                        <Route path='/db/devices-history' component={DeviHistory} />
                    </Switch>
                </MainLayout>
                {/* </Route> */}

            </Switch>
        </Router>
    )
}
